T02D2321:263b-1: bo dhi tsar+ya pra d'i pa n'a ma /
T02D2321:263b-3: byang chub spyod pa'i sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02D2321:264a-2: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal nas //
T02D2321:264a-3: dam pa skyes mchog rnams la 'dud //
T02D2321:264a-4: 'gro ba sdug bsngal gdungs pa la //
T02D2321:264a-5: zhi byed bsil ldan dri med bshad //
T02D2321:264a-8: lo zla tshes grangs 'chi dang nye //
T02D2321:264a-9: bu tsha la sogs grogs rnams dang //
T02D2321:264a-10: bor nas gcig pu 'gro dgos nas //
T02D2321:264a-11: bar do bzhi las 'chi ba'i tshe //
T02D2321:264a-12: sdug bsngal ri bos mnan pas sdug / bdun tsho bdun du bar do ru //
T02D2321:264a-13: gshed pos 'tshe zhing sdug re bsngal //
T02D2321:264a-14: ma rig 'khrul pas lus blangs te //
T02D2321:264a-15: nyon mongs lnga yis sems kyang dkrugs //
T02D2321:264a-16: dper na shing rta'i 'khor lo bzhin //
T02D2321:264a-17: 'gro ba drug gi sdug bsngal myong //
T02D2321:264a-18: sdug bsngal bzhi sogs sdug bsngal bas //
T02D2321:264a-19: de phyir byang chub bsgrub par bya //
T02D2321:264a-20: le lo g-yeng ba rab spangs te //
T02D2321:264a-21: shes rab gsum la blo sbyangs la //
T02D2321:264a-22: rtag tu dur khrod gnas su 'dug //
T02D2321:264a-23: dran pa bzhi dang ldan pa yis //
T02D2321:264a-24: tho rangs langs te khrus byas la //
T02D2321:264a-25: dad dang mos gus sngon btang ste //
T02D2321:264a-26: byang chub sems dang rab ldan pas //
T02D2321:264a-27: 'gro ba bu bzhin gdung bar bya //
T02D2321:264a-28: gsum la skyabs 'gro ma nyams bya //
T02D2321:264a-29: bden pa'i chos la the tshom spang //
T02D2321:264a-30: 'dod pa spel phyir chu sbyin gtang //
T02D2321:264a-31: mchod bshags la sogs kha ton bya //
T02D2321:264a-32: gru yi tshul du lus kyang btsal //
T02D2321:264a-33: bag yod spyod lam blo gros zab //
T02D2321:264a-34: lha dang mi 'bral bsam pa bzang //
T02D2321:264a-35: dang po byung bas dkon mchog mchod //
T02D2321:264a-36: kha zas kun las rnal 'byor bya //
T02D2321:264a-37: lhag ma 'byung po rnams la bsngo //
T02D2321:264a-38: bshad gci rnams kyang spyin par gtang //
T02D2321:264a-39: smon lam rgya chen gdab pa'o //
T02D2321:264a-40: chos su 'gro ba'i tshig kyang brjod //
T02D2321:264a-41: s'atstsha gdab cing srog kyang gdon //
T02D2321:264a-42: bsod nams tshogs ni ci nus bsags //
T02D2321:264a-43: ye shes tshogs kyang de bzhin te //
T02D2321:264a-44: sdom pa gsum dang ldan par bya //
T02D2321:264a-45: pha rol phyin pa drug spyad de //
T02D2321:264a-46: dbang bzhi rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor bya //
T02D2321:264a-47: bskor ba bya zhing lus kyang bcag /'byung ba bzhi ni ro snyoms te //
T02D2321:264a-48: mtshan mo nang gi spyad pa bya //
T02D2321:264a-49: srod la gtor tshogs chen po gtang //
T02D2321:264b-0: nam phyed @264b tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor //
T02D2321:264b-1: phyi bcud nang bcud rang sor gzhag / nam smad
T02D2321:264b-2: dge ba'i gnyid kyang log / spyod lam rnam bzhi'i
T02D2321:264b-3: chos la bsdu // ma yengs chu bo'i rgyun ltar spyad //
T02D2321:264b-4: sgyu lus 'od gsal bsre ba yang //
T02D2321:264b-5: sum cu rtsa bzhi'i gdams pa'i don //
T02D2321:264b-6: sems nyid las su rung bas ni //
T02D2321:264b-7: rang dbang rgyal po sems la thob //
T02D2321:264b-8: de phri rnal 'bro brtson par spyad //
T02D2321:264b-9: byang chub spyod pa'i sgron ma zhes bya ba rje
T02D2321:264b-10: btsun ka ma la sh'i las mdzad pa rdzogs so
T02D2321:264b-12: / // / pandi ta kha che dzny'a na gu hya dang /
